Package: UKCensusAPI
Title: Automated Query and Download of UK Census Data
Version: 1.1.6
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Smith", email = "a.p.smith@leeds.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides an R interface to the www.nomisweb.co.uk census data API. It enables:
    - querying table metadata
    - autogenerating customised python and R query code for future use
    - automated cached data downloads
    - easily modifying the geography of existing queries
    - adding descriptive information to tables (from metadata)
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
Imports:
  reticulate,
  testthat,
License: MIT + file LICENCE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
